  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.3">
<l>āyar koḻuntā yavarāl puṭaiyuṇṇum</l>
<l>māyap pirāṉaiyeṉ māṇikkac cōtiyait</l>
<l>tūya vamutaip parukipparuki yeṉ</l>
<l>māyap piṟavi mayarvaṟut tēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Drinking in [and] drinking in the pure ambrosia,</l>
<l>my ruby light, the lord of illusion</l>
<l>who, as the sprout of the cowherd clan, was thrashed by them,</l>
<l>I have cut off the confusion of my illusory [re]birth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
